companyName: AB Svensk Ekportkredit (Swedish Export Credit Corporation) ELEMENTS Linked to the MLCX Grains Index - Total Return
description:
The investment seeks to replicate, net of expenses, the MLCX Grains Total Return Index.
 The index is designed reflect the performance of a fully collateralized investment in the four exchange-traded futures contracts on four physical commodities: corn, soybeans, soy meal and wheat.
